query:
/*+ NoMergeJoin(ci n mk) NoNestLoop(ci mk n k) NoHashJoin(ci k mk n t) */ select min(k.keyword) AS movie_keyword,
min(n.name) AS actor_name,
min(t.title) AS hero_movie
from name AS n
inner join cast_info AS ci
on n.id = ci.person_id AND n.name like '%Alex%'
inner join movie_keyword AS mk
on ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
inner join keyword AS k
on k.id = mk.keyword_id AND k.keyword IN ('tv-special',
'violence',
'based-on-novel',
'violence',
'murder',
'hospital',
'hero',
'based-on-comic')
inner join title AS t
on t.id = mk.movie_id AND t.id = ci.movie_id AND t.production_year > 1995;
